In addition, all of the staff of the Saturday section the fares and lunch.
With regard to the fact that the overtime the most pressing and most burning point demands and complaints of trade unionists, who had the last week, the production has the management yesterday afternoon with immediate effect on the lifting of all overtime for the month of December, Vank.
