The history of South Africa, says Morgan Freeman alias Nelson Mandela
In the next few days, the new Hollywood film Clint East Woods in American cinema " Invictus: the Ungeschlagene ", which is part of the life history of the former President of the Republic of South Africa, Nelsona Mandela.
The role of the world - famous fighter against apartheid, Morgan Freeman, a few years ago allegedly by Mandela himself.
The supporting players role of the legendary South African champions in rugby, Francois Pienaar, Matt Damon.
With the launch of the film will also be reactions of critics and the public.
Nelson Mandela
With whole name means he Nelson Rolihlaha Mandela, born on 18 July 1918 in South African Mvez.
