Brazil called a date to leave
The Brazilian government has set the residence of Manuel Zelaya in its embassy in Tegucigalpa a deadline.
The President must be removed from the diplomatic representation at the latest on 27 January, when his mandate expires officially
Francisco Catunda, trade delegates of the Brazilian embassy in the Honduran capital, confirmed the TV Globo that " Mel " knows that before this date the message, in which he had found since 21 September asylum must have left.
" He is aware that he must go on 27 January, as his mandate expires on that day and he needs to find a new accommodation. "
The station also quoted the ex - president, who confirmed his intention to leave the message before the date: " My position is to go as soon as possible, with the backing of the government of Brazil, " Zelaya said on the phone.
After the elections on 29 November (where Porfirio Lobo emerged as the victor) assured Zelaya that he will stay until January in the Brazilian embassy.
However, this week, he tried to obtain refuge in Brazil.
This, however, the refusal Zelayas, the status of an asylum seeker politician, the " de facto " government headed by Roberto Micheletti.
Thank you!
After the glowing days since last spring, in which the inflation of assets was the prevailing mood in the markets, is back on the uncertainty in the markets, which is not surprising, since this is their natural state, in an environment in which the broker decisions on an inherently uncertain future.
The measure used to stabilize the markets, it was to pay off the debt with the direct purchase of assets and indirectly the liquidity free rein in interest rates, the move to zero, so that in this way the assets to the banks.
The central banks have already confirmed that the direct purchases of assets as well as ended and, without their heterodox policy to liquidity in question, start to throw a spanner in the works, as the BCE näc already with its annual auction, which takes place next week.
That is why investors have doubts about the ability of the world economy, the economic recovery without these heterodox measures and we are currently witnessing a reversal in the reduction of risk premiums.
The volatility of the stock markets and the differences in corporate bonuses rise again, even if they are still a long way from the para - normal amounts they reached at the beginning of the year.
The states have been forced to nationalize the private risks and the national debt will rise again.
It is now back on quality and the United States, Japan and Germany are the favorite refuge of investors, which in turn leads to an increase of the differences of the countries in the euro zone in regard to Germany.
Spain has been barely affected by this episode of instability, but then came Standard& Poor's and threatened with a new revision downwards on the assessment of Spain.
On the other hand, does not harm a degree of uncertainty for the defenders of the moral hazard had tried again, with the leaders of the world economic policy, an awareness of what had caused them to produce, since the devastating effects of the restriction of loans to the loss of jobs, had slowed down, as they should have adopted a new day thanks to action.
