Nueva Rumasa offers 61 million for 29.9% participation in Sos
The group Nueva Rumasa yesterday details leaked to the purchase offer of shares, with a limit of between 25 and 29.9% of Sos wants to buy.
A percentage, because of the number of shares, not to make a public tender (opa) .
The concrete offers Nueva Rumasa 1,5025 euros per share, to be paid out In ten years and with an interest rate of 1% per year because of this shift.
Yesterday, the Sos shares closed with 1.85 euro, Nueva Rumasa assessed the company 18% below the market value.
According to Nuevan Rumasa reflects the price of 1.50 euros the real assessment of Sos.
The offer is associated with the appointment of eight of the 15 advisers.
The group from Jeréz gives shareholders a deadline of 15 days to their interest in the sale of their shares.
CNMV assured that it was not informed about this offer, although the company confirmed that it was entered into contact with the authority.
In conclusion, the payment would amount to 611.7 million, while the value of Sos 254,27 million.
Meanwhile, Sos structured its business to continue.
