The purpose of this purchase, it was to offer its customers more services and value, with the possibility to gain access to a riesigeen international market.
This Begutachtungs and purchasing service is exclusively to industry professionals, such as insurance companies, consultants, car rental companies, workshops, scrapyards and car dealers, who must register their activities.
This platform was founded in 1996 in Germany and manages more than 650,000 operations across Europe, 500,000 of them in Germany alone.
Its main markets are Spain, Greece, Poland and Turkey.
The website has more than 1,500 registered sellers and 4,000 consultants.
Every day, 3,000 ads and on the Spanish market every day, 100 new ads.
According to the Spanish legislation, a vehicle whose Fahrgestellnumer abgemeldet, was no longer on the streets, it must not be used, however, certain damaged parts as spare parts.
The cars with historical value must be approved again, even if they were after difficult authorities abgemeldet.
Cost estimates of the workshop in four stages
With the tool Auda Taller, the company Audatex ensures that the user in only four stages a cost estimate: identification of the vehicle, search of spare parts, and a cost estimate.
The ease of use of these systems is a fundamental condition, especially in order to convince the older professionals, who are usually more or less against the use of this new computer techniques.
The database includes 1.034 vehicles, 666 of them passenger cars, 109 SUVs, 137 motorcycles, 78 vans and trucks.
Of course, you need to use a computer with Internet connection.
After the repair model based on the chassis number have been identified, is a chart of the model and will be needed spare parts.
The user can variables, such as the price for the working hours, Aufpreise or rebates and then he can leave the cost estimates and pass on to its customers.
AudaTaller, however, is not a tool for evaluating how AudaPlus, but rather a reference list.
The main difference between the two systems is that the focus on dieWerkstatt no estimated working hours.
The use of this tool for 350 euros per year, an amount that can pay for the customer.
At the time, the company to be able to offer these images into three - dimensional format.
It is an innovation in the auto mechanics can wait for a long time, with her, for example, a door and the picture can, to the inner side.
